snippet: At least 11 students have been killed in violent clashes with Ethiopian police in a region that has long been the scene of a secessionist movement, the government said late Thursday.
lead_paragraph: At least 11 students have been killed in violent clashes with Ethiopian police in a region that has long been the scene of a secessionist movement, the government said late Thursday.

headline.main: Ethiopia: Student Protesters Killed in Clashes With Police
